	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Okay so I found my problem...I was incorrectly determining page-boundary crossing cases of the indexed addressing modes.
<br />
<br />I'd still like to find a trusted opcode cycle count reference, though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


